snippet.textDisplay: I have been waiting for Ahmed Jahanzeb's performance in COKE STUDIO :) Here he comes with a BANG, The uniqueness of his voice has made this song really special.  Every time he sings the LINK LINE adding new flavor to it. He's done justice to it. His lyrics are shorter comparatively BUT the quality is HIGH. Not underestimating the other guy (Umair Jaswal) But when Ahmed sings: Umair's part is forgotten, The song belongs to him undoutedely.  In my personal opinion, it would be a great really unfortunate not to utilize his voice as PLAYBACK singer in INDO-PAK. My best wishes and prayers for his upcoming projects. RESPECT AND LOVE
